   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Story Prompt Expander\\n\",\"**NLP Project 59 of 100** — Turn one-line prompts into full story setups using LLMs.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import requests\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"prompts = [\\n    'A detective discovers their partner is the criminal.',\\n    'The last human on Earth hears a knock at the door.',\\n    'A time traveler accidentally prevents their own birth.',\\n]\\n\\ndef expand_prompt(prompt, model='qwen3:1.7b'):\\n    full_prompt = f'Expand this one-line story prompt into a 3-paragraph story setup. Include setting, character, and conflict.\\\\n\\\\nPrompt: {prompt} /no_think'\\n    try:\\n        r = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate',json={'model':model,'prompt':full_prompt,'stream':False},timeout=60)\\n        return r.json().get('response','')\\n    except:\\n        return f'Setting: A dark, rainy city at midnight.\\\\nCharacter: {prompt.split()[1] if len(prompt.split())>1 else \\\"The protagonist\\\"} stands at a crossroads.\\\\nConflict: {prompt}\\\\n\\\\n[Expand this with a local LLM for full story setup.]'\\n\\nfor p in prompts:\\n    print(f'📝 Prompt: {p}')\\n    print(f'📖 Expanded:\\\\n{expand_prompt(p)}')\\n    print('---\\\\n')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **LLMs excel at creative expansion** from minimal input.\\n\",\"- **Structured prompts (setting, character, conflict)** improve output quality.\\n\",\"- **For writing tools, offer multiple variations** and let users pick.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
